We cannot afford a party split. We have agreed to the demands, and will now be forced to abandon our efforts to court the parties to our right.

German Democracy is shaken by this affair. The <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span>, the driver of democracy and stability within the <span style="color: #000000;">We</span><span style="color: #DD0000;">im</span><span style="color: #FFCC00;">ar</span> system, has been lost to radical movements. Our actions will be extremely limited by our elements on the <span style="color: #AF0202;">Left</span>.


@oppose
